snippet.title: Zossed in Space  -  video game 1981
snippet.description:
Zossed in Space is a 1981 video game published by Adventure International for the TRS-80.

Gameplay
Zossed in Space is a game in which the player accumulates trading units and destroys enemy ships in various sectors of space.
